'''香港国际安全与无害环境拆船公约'''（{{lang-en|Hong Kong International Convention for the Safe and Environmentally Sound Recycling of Ships}}）是2009年[[国际海事组织|国际海事组织]]制订的公约，目前尚未生效。该公约旨在确保船舶达到使用寿命后被回收时，不会对人类健康安全和环境造成不必要风险。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Hong Kong International Convention for the Safe and Environmentally Sound Recycling of Ships|url=https://www.imo.org/en/About/Conventions/Pages/The-Hong-Kong-International-Convention-for-the-Safe-and-Environmentally-Sound-Recycling-of-Ships.aspx|accessdate=2021-03-19|work=www.imo.org}}</ref>

